snippet.title: Zueirama - Trailer / Indie Game 2019
snippet.description: Zueirama is a fun action adventure game packed with references to memes and Zueira. Inspired by the games of the 90s, with cartoon characters that reflect the essence and Brazilian swinging like you have never seen.
